query:
SELECT id as "id!: i32", 
address as "address!: String", 
balance as "balance!: String", 
last_auto_paid_cycle as "last_auto_paid_cycle!: String", 
is_contract as "is_contract!: bool", 
estimated_total_doc_claimed as "estimated_total_doc_claimed!: String" FROM holders WHERE (NOT $1::boolean OR id = $2::int4) AND (NOT $3::boolean OR id = ANY(CAST($4 as int4[])) ) AND (NOT $5::boolean OR address = $6::varchar) AND (NOT $7::boolean OR address ILIKE $8::varchar) AND (NOT $9::boolean OR balance = $10::varchar) AND (NOT $11::boolean OR last_auto_paid_cycle = $12::varchar) AND (NOT $13::boolean OR last_auto_paid_cycle < $14::varchar) AND (NOT $15::boolean OR is_contract = $16::boolean) AND (NOT $17::boolean OR estimated_total_doc_claimed = $18::varchar) ORDER BY 
      (CASE ($19 = 'Id' AND NOT $20) WHEN true THEN id ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($19 = 'Id' AND $20) WHEN true THEN id ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($19 = 'Address' AND NOT $20) WHEN true THEN address ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($19 = 'Address' AND $20) WHEN true THEN address ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($19 = 'Balance' AND NOT $20) WHEN true THEN balance ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($19 = 'Balance' AND $20) WHEN true THEN balance ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($19 = 'LastAutoPaidCycle' AND NOT $20) WHEN true THEN last_auto_paid_cycle ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($19 = 'LastAutoPaidCycle' AND $20) WHEN true THEN last_auto_paid_cycle ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($19 = 'IsContract' AND NOT $20) WHEN true THEN is_contract ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($19 = 'IsContract' AND $20) WHEN true THEN is_contract ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($19 = 'EstimatedTotalDocClaimed' AND NOT $20) WHEN true THEN estimated_total_doc_claimed ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($19 = 'EstimatedTotalDocClaimed' AND $20) WHEN true THEN estimated_total_doc_claimed ELSE NULL END) DESC
     LIMIT $21 OFFSET $22
